// ProcessWire CMS update example using CLI\n// Backup your site before performing updates\n\n// Step 1: Download the latest ProcessWire version\nwget https://github.com/processwire/processwire/archive/master.zip\n\n// Step 2: Unzip the downloaded file\nunzip master.zip\n\n// Step 3: Copy the new files to your ProcessWire installation\ncp -r processwire-master/* /path/to/your/site/\n\n// Step 4: Run any necessary database updates via the admin panel